%% Diagram: RFC 8767 serve-stale fallback when authoritative servers are unreachable
%% Type: sequence
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant R as Resolver
    participant A as Auth

    Note over R: Cached record\nTTL expired 4 h ago
    C->>R: Q: api A?
    Note over R: 1.8 s timer
    R->>A: forward
    Note right of A: Timeout
    Note over R: 1.8 s elapsed
    R-->>C: stale (TTL 30 s)
    R->>A: bg retry
    A-->>R: SERVFAIL
    Note over R: 30 s recheck
    Note over C,R: Service stays up
